<hr data-start="147" data-end="150">
<h2 data-section-id="18i77mc" data-start="152" data-end="188">🎓 <strong data-start="158" data-end="188">SLIDE 1 – JUDUL PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="j04leu" data-start="189" data-end="306"><strong data-start="193" data-end="306">PENGARUH MEDIA SOSIAL INSTAGRAM DAN WHATSAPP TERHADAP PEMBENTUKAN BUDAYA “ALONE TOGETHER” DI UNIVERSITAS RIAU</strong></h3>
<p data-start="308" data-end="395"><strong data-start="308" data-end="327">Nama Peneliti :</strong> [Nama Kamu]<br data-start="339" data-end="342">
<strong data-start="342" data-end="357">Institusi :</strong> Universitas Riau<br data-start="374" data-end="377">
<strong data-start="377" data-end="388">Tahun :</strong> 2025</p>
<hr data-start="397" data-end="400">
<h2 data-section-id="1i5uzyk" data-start="402" data-end="436">💡 <strong data-start="408" data-end="436">SLIDE 2 – LATAR BELAKANG</strong></h2>
<ul data-start="437" data-end="1064">
<li data-section-id="1irunh0" data-start="437" data-end="529">
<p data-start="439" data-end="529">Di era globalisasi, kemajuan teknologi informasi dan komunikasi berkembang sangat pesat.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="868syl" data-start="530" data-end="631">
<p data-start="532" data-end="631">Media sosial seperti <strong data-start="553" data-end="579">Instagram dan WhatsApp</strong> menjadi bagian penting dalam kehidupan mahasiswa.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qmhx9w" data-start="632" data-end="798">
<p data-start="634" data-end="798">Meskipun media sosial mempermudah komunikasi dan berbagi informasi, penggunaannya yang berlebihan <strong data-start="732" data-end="768">menyebabkan fenomena sosial baru</strong> yaitu <strong data-start="775" data-end="795">“Alone Together”</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="crqi9j" data-start="799" data-end="969">
<p data-start="801" data-end="969">Fenomena ini menggambarkan kondisi di mana seseorang <strong data-start="854" data-end="889">secara fisik bersama orang lain</strong>, tetapi <strong data-start="898" data-end="930">secara psikologis terisolasi</strong> karena fokus pada perangkat digital.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zt28ot" data-start="970" data-end="1064">
<p data-start="972" data-end="1064">Kondisi tersebut kini banyak ditemukan di lingkungan kampus, termasuk di Universitas Riau.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1066" data-end="1069">
<h2 data-section-id="1rvua6f" data-start="1071" data-end="1126">🎯 <strong data-start="1077" data-end="1126">SLIDE 3 – RUMUSAN MASALAH &amp; TUJUAN PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="70p3es" data-start="1127" data-end="1151"><strong data-start="1131" data-end="1151">Rumusan Masalah:</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="1152" data-end="1280">
<li data-section-id="mugwi9" data-start="1152" data-end="1280">
<p data-start="1155" data-end="1280">Seberapa besar pengaruh media sosial Instagram dan WhatsApp terhadap pembentukan budaya “Alone Together” di Universitas Riau?</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="1cnpl5w" data-start="1282" data-end="1308"><strong data-start="1286" data-end="1308">Tujuan Penelitian:</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="1309" data-end="1607">
<li data-section-id="c6rbqp" data-start="1309" data-end="1399">
<p data-start="1312" data-end="1399">Mengetahui sejauh mana penggunaan media sosial memengaruhi perilaku sosial mahasiswa.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ill7zp" data-start="1400" data-end="1507">
<p data-start="1403" data-end="1507">Menganalisis hubungan antara intensitas penggunaan media sosial dan munculnya budaya “Alone Together”.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a7fdza" data-start="1508" data-end="1607">
<p data-start="1511" data-end="1607">Memberikan gambaran tentang dampak media sosial terhadap interaksi sosial mahasiswa di kampus.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1609" data-end="1612">
<h2 data-section-id="10vu5mi" data-start="1614" data-end="1651">🧪 <strong data-start="1620" data-end="1651">SLIDE 4 – METODE PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1k2vp66" data-start="1652" data-end="1679"><strong data-start="1656" data-end="1677">Jenis Penelitian:</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1680" data-end="1706"><strong data-start="1680" data-end="1706">Kuantitatif Deskriptif</strong></p>
<h3 data-section-id="12573jy" data-start="1708" data-end="1740"><strong data-start="1712" data-end="1738">Pendekatan Penelitian:</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1741" data-end="1986">
<li data-section-id="wo7fh" data-start="1741" data-end="1861">
<p data-start="1743" data-end="1861">Menggunakan <strong data-start="1755" data-end="1781">pendekatan kuantitatif</strong> karena mengandalkan <strong data-start="1802" data-end="1859">angka, data statistik, dan hasil pengujian hipotesis.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hhijoc" data-start="1862" data-end="1986">
<p data-start="1864" data-end="1986">Data diperoleh melalui <strong data-start="1887" data-end="1911">penyebaran kuesioner</strong> dengan skala <strong data-start="1925" data-end="1935">Likert</strong> kepada 100 responden mahasiswa Universitas Riau.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="9cg8rc" data-start="1988" data-end="2019"><strong data-start="1992" data-end="2017">Teknik Analisis Data:</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="2020" data-end="2291">
<li data-section-id="ympazd" data-start="2020" data-end="2090">
<p data-start="2022" data-end="2090"><strong data-start="2022" data-end="2056">Uji Validitas dan Reliabilitas</strong> untuk mengukur keakuratan data.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ez072r" data-start="2091" data-end="2169">
<p data-start="2093" data-end="2169"><strong data-start="2093" data-end="2125">Uji Regresi Linier Sederhana</strong> untuk mengetahui pengaruh antar variabel.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vfy9wn" data-start="2170" data-end="2291">
<p data-start="2172" data-end="2291"><strong data-start="2172" data-end="2208">Uji t dan Koefisien Korelasi (R)</strong> untuk melihat hubungan signifikan antara media sosial dan budaya Alone Together.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2293" data-end="2296">
<h2 data-section-id="535jf9" data-start="2298" data-end="2334">📊 <strong data-start="2304" data-end="2334">SLIDE 5 – HASIL PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="16z3b7v" data-start="2335" data-end="2363"><strong data-start="2339" data-end="2363">Hasil Uji Statistik:</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="2364" data-end="2794">
<li data-section-id="ru3xvk" data-start="2364" data-end="2504">
<p data-start="2366" data-end="2504">Nilai <strong data-start="2372" data-end="2410">t-hitung (4,364) &gt; t-tabel (3,920)</strong><br data-start="2410" data-end="2413">
→ Artinya terdapat <strong data-start="2434" data-end="2457">pengaruh signifikan</strong> media sosial terhadap budaya Alone Together.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gx31t0" data-start="2505" data-end="2619">
<p data-start="2507" data-end="2619">Nilai <strong data-start="2513" data-end="2526">R = 0,403</strong>, menunjukkan <strong data-start="2540" data-end="2559">hubungan sedang</strong> antara penggunaan media sosial dan budaya Alone Together.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1y4yqv0" data-start="2620" data-end="2794">
<p data-start="2622" data-end="2794">Nilai <strong data-start="2628" data-end="2642">R² = 0,163</strong>, berarti <strong data-start="2652" data-end="2695">16,3% pembentukan budaya Alone Together</strong> dipengaruhi oleh penggunaan Instagram dan WhatsApp, sedangkan <strong data-start="2758" data-end="2792">83,7% dipengaruhi faktor lain.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="19zibin" data-start="2796" data-end="2823"><strong data-start="2800" data-end="2823">Interpretasi Hasil:</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="2824" data-end="3055">
<li data-section-id="y1y81h" data-start="2824" data-end="2941">
<p data-start="2826" data-end="2941">Semakin sering mahasiswa menggunakan media sosial, semakin besar kecenderungan mengalami fenomena Alone Together.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mkeqx6" data-start="2942" data-end="3055">
<p data-start="2944" data-end="3055">Media sosial menciptakan <strong data-start="2969" data-end="2988">ilusi kedekatan</strong>, tetapi justru <strong data-start="3004" data-end="3053">mengurangi interaksi langsung antar individu.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3057" data-end="3060">
<h2 data-section-id="kc9n2u" data-start="3062" data-end="3100">🧩 <strong data-start="3068" data-end="3100">SLIDE 6 – KESIMPULAN &amp; SARAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="14po1kz" data-start="3101" data-end="3120"><strong data-start="3105" data-end="3120">Kesimpulan:</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="3121" data-end="3598">
<li data-section-id="m7cgc1" data-start="3121" data-end="3252">
<p data-start="3124" data-end="3252">Media sosial Instagram dan WhatsApp <strong data-start="3160" data-end="3186">berpengaruh signifikan</strong> terhadap pembentukan budaya Alone Together di Universitas Riau.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mxmho0" data-start="3253" data-end="3364">
<p data-start="3256" data-end="3364">Pengaruh tersebut termasuk dalam kategori <strong data-start="3298" data-end="3317">hubungan sedang</strong>, artinya ada efek nyata namun tidak dominan.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s9mo32" data-start="3365" data-end="3477">
<p data-start="3368" data-end="3477">Media sosial telah mengubah pola komunikasi mahasiswa — dari interaksi langsung menjadi komunikasi virtual.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yycggr" data-start="3478" data-end="3598">
<p data-start="3481" data-end="3598">Mahasiswa lebih sering <strong data-start="3504" data-end="3535">asyik dengan gawai (gadget)</strong> dibandingkan berinteraksi dengan lingkungan sosial sekitarnya.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="68nh77" data-start="3600" data-end="3614"><strong data-start="3604" data-end="3614">Saran:</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="3615" data-end="3895">
<li data-section-id="1opaqbi" data-start="3615" data-end="3698">
<p data-start="3617" data-end="3698">Mahasiswa perlu <strong data-start="3633" data-end="3696">menyeimbangkan komunikasi digital dan interaksi tatap muka.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gn59ac" data-start="3699" data-end="3809">
<p data-start="3701" data-end="3809">Perguruan tinggi dapat <strong data-start="3724" data-end="3768">mendorong kegiatan sosial dan organisasi</strong> untuk meningkatkan interaksi langsung.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1335t9f" data-start="3810" data-end="3895">
<p data-start="3812" data-end="3895">Perlu edukasi digital agar media sosial digunakan <strong data-start="3862" data-end="3893">secara bijak dan produktif.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3897" data-end="3900">
<h2 data-section-id="p4enr7" data-start="3902" data-end="3938">📚 <strong data-start="3908" data-end="3938">SLIDE 7 – JENIS PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="3z6mvh" data-start="3939" data-end="3969"><strong data-start="3943" data-end="3969">Kuantitatif Deskriptif</strong></h3>
<p data-start="3970" data-end="3985"><strong data-start="3970" data-end="3985">Penjelasan:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="3986" data-end="4383">
<li data-section-id="i0fzr3" data-start="3986" data-end="4103">
<p data-start="3988" data-end="4103">Disebut <strong data-start="3996" data-end="4011">kuantitatif</strong> karena menggunakan data numerik (angka), uji statistik, dan hasil penghitungan matematis.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15wgen6" data-start="4104" data-end="4244">
<p data-start="4106" data-end="4244">Disebut <strong data-start="4114" data-end="4128">deskriptif</strong> karena menjelaskan fenomena sosial (Alone Together) berdasarkan data yang diperoleh, tanpa memanipulasi variabel.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uis74q" data-start="4245" data-end="4383">
<p data-start="4247" data-end="4383">Tujuannya untuk <strong data-start="4263" data-end="4310">menggambarkan secara sistematis dan faktual</strong> hubungan antara penggunaan media sosial dan perilaku sosial mahasiswa.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4385" data-end="4388">
<h2 data-section-id="zdxmyu" data-start="4390" data-end="4426">🧠 <strong data-start="4396" data-end="4426">SLIDE 8 – MAKNA PENELITIAN</strong></h2>
<ul data-start="4427" data-end="4788">
<li data-section-id="17limvr" data-start="4427" data-end="4541">
<p data-start="4429" data-end="4541">Kemajuan teknologi membawa manfaat besar dalam komunikasi, tetapi juga <strong data-start="4500" data-end="4539">menghadirkan tantangan sosial baru.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ct3agx" data-start="4542" data-end="4657">
<p data-start="4544" data-end="4657">Budaya Alone Together menunjukkan bahwa <strong data-start="4584" data-end="4655">teknologi bisa memperluas jarak sosial di tengah kedekatan digital.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="apcli8" data-start="4658" data-end="4788">
<p data-start="4660" data-end="4788">Diperlukan <strong data-start="4671" data-end="4705">kesadaran dan literasi digital</strong> agar mahasiswa tidak kehilangan kemampuan komunikasi langsung dan empati sosial.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4790" data-end="4793">
<p data-start="4795" data-end="4827">Kalau kamu mau, saya bisa bantu:</p>
<ul data-start="4828" data-end="5053" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="18i8xz6" data-start="4828" data-end="5053" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="4830" data-end="5053" data-is-last-node="">💾 Buatkan <strong data-start="4841" data-end="4868">file PowerPoint (.pptx)</strong> dari isi di atas dengan desain akademik rapi (warna biru atau hijau kampus, font profesional, dan pembagian visual data).<br data-start="4990" data-end="4993">
Apakah kamu ingin saya buatkan file PowerPoint-nya langsung?</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http