4-49bd-a934-55e233858ea3" data-testid="conversation-turn-19" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h5 class="sr-only select-none">You said:</h5><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="84870004-bf24-49bd-a934-55e233858ea3" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="user-message-bubble-color corner-superellipse/0.98 relative rounded-[22px] px-4 py-2.5 leading-6 max-w-(--user-chat-width,70%)"><div class="whitespace-pre-wrap">berikan saya draf surat permohonab tindak lanjut / klarifikasi laporan ke divpropam polda</div></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="e35a7b90-bfa6-4cbf-8ef0-4154c701181d" data-testid="conversation-turn-20" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e35a7b90-bfa6-4cbf-8ef0-4154c701181d" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="326">Berikut contoh <strong data-start="15" data-end="93">draf surat permohonan tindak lanjut/klarifikasi laporan ke Divpropam Polda</strong> yang bisa kamu sesuaikan dengan kebutuhanmu (nama, tanggal, nomor laporan, dan kronologi).<br data-start="184" data-end="187">
Format ini menggunakan <strong data-start="210" data-end="260">struktur resmi dan bahasa birokrasi kepolisian</strong>, jadi bisa langsung dipakai atau disunting untuk surat nyata 👇</p>
<hr data-start="328" data-end="331">
<p data-start="333" data-end="454"><strong data-start="333" data-end="357">KOP SURAT (bila ada)</strong><br data-start="357" data-end="360">
<em data-start="360" data-end="452">(Jika pribadi, bagian ini bisa dihapus dan diganti dengan identitas pribadi di awal surat)</em></p>
<hr data-start="456" data-end="459">
<h3 data-section-id="8b4z1v" data-start="461" data-end="523"><strong data-start="465" data-end="521">SURAT PERMOHONAN TINDAK LANJUT / KLARIFIKASI LAPORAN</strong></h3>
<p data-start="524" data-end="540">Nomor: ………………………</p>
<p data-start="542" data-end="672">Kepada Yth.<br data-start="553" data-end="556">
<strong data-start="556" data-end="608">Kepala Divisi Profesi dan Pengamanan (Divpropam)</strong><br data-start="608" data-end="611">
<strong data-start="611" data-end="654">Kepolisian Daerah [Nama Daerah / Polda]</strong><br data-start="654" data-end="657">
di –<br data-start="661" data-end="664">
Tempat</p>
<p data-start="674" data-end="690">Dengan hormat,</p>
<p data-start="692" data-end="733">Saya yang bertanda tangan di bawah ini:</p>
<p data-start="735" data-end="998"><strong data-start="735" data-end="743">Nama</strong>             : [Nama Lengkap Anda]<br data-start="777" data-end="780">
<strong data-start="780" data-end="800">Tempat/Tgl Lahir</strong> : [Tempat, Tanggal Lahir]<br data-start="826" data-end="829">
<strong data-start="829" data-end="839">Alamat</strong>            : [Alamat Lengkap]<br data-start="869" data-end="872">
<strong data-start="872" data-end="884">Nomor HP</strong>          : [Nomor Telepon yang bisa dihubungi]<br data-start="931" data-end="934">
<strong data-start="934" data-end="947">Pekerjaan</strong>         : [Pekerjaan / Mahasiswa / Swasta, dst.]</p>
<p data-start="1000" data-end="1180">Dengan ini bermaksud untuk <strong data-start="1027" data-end="1066">memohon tindak lanjut / klarifikasi</strong> atas laporan yang telah saya sampaikan kepada <strong data-start="1113" data-end="1146">Divpropam Polda [Nama Daerah]</strong> dengan rincian sebagai berikut:</p>
<ul data-start="1182" data-end="1439">
<li data-section-id="z9uuql" data-start="1182" data-end="1247">
<p data-start="1184" data-end="1247"><strong data-start="1184" data-end="1201">Nomor Laporan</strong> : [Nomor laporan pengaduan, jika sudah ada]</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pjfdzk" data-start="1248" data-end="1302">
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1302"><strong data-start="1250" data-end="1269">Tanggal Laporan</strong> : [Tanggal laporan diserahkan]</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lby5jp" data-start="1303" data-end="1439">
<p data-start="1305" data-end="1439"><strong data-start="1305" data-end="1324">Perihal Laporan</strong> : [Contoh: Dugaan pelanggaran kode etik oleh anggota Polri / Permintaan klarifikasi terhadap penanganan laporan]</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1441" data-end="1702">Adapun maksud dari surat ini adalah untuk menanyakan perkembangan penanganan laporan tersebut, serta memohon agar kiranya <strong data-start="1563" data-end="1668">pihak Divpropam Polda dapat memberikan penjelasan atau klarifikasi resmi terkait proses tindak lanjut</strong> yang telah atau akan dilakukan.</p>
<p data-start="1704" data-end="1989">Saya berharap laporan yang telah disampaikan dapat segera diproses sesuai dengan ketentuan hukum dan peraturan yang berlaku di lingkungan Kepolisian Negara Republik Indonesia, sebagai wujud transparansi dan profesionalitas institusi Polri dalam menangani setiap pengaduan masyarakat.</p>
<p data-start="1991" data-end="2054">Sebagai bahan pertimbangan, bersama surat ini saya lampirkan:</p>
<ol data-start="2055" data-end="2198">
<li data-section-id="g9imd3" data-start="2055" data-end="2096">
<p data-start="2058" data-end="2096">Fotokopi Kartu Tanda Penduduk (KTP);</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qike5r" data-start="2097" data-end="2157">
<p data-start="2100" data-end="2157">Fotokopi tanda bukti penerimaan laporan dari Divpropam;</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="25ycoq" data-start="2158" data-end="2198">
<p data-start="2161" data-end="2198">Bukti pendukung lainnya (jika ada).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="2200" data-end="2406">Demikian surat permohonan ini saya sampaikan. Besar harapan saya agar dapat diberikan penjelasan resmi mengenai tindak lanjut laporan dimaksud. Atas perhatian dan kerja samanya, saya ucapkan terima kasih.</p>
<p data-start="2408" data-end="2422">Hormat saya,</p>
<p data-start="2427" data-end="2485"><em data-start="2427" data-end="2447">(Materai Rp10.000)</em><br data-start="2447" data-end="2450">
<strong data-start="2450" data-end="2483">[Tanda tangan dan nama jelas]</strong></p>
<p data-start="2487" data-end="2508">[Nama Lengkap Anda]</p>
<hr data-start="2510" data-end="2513">
<h3 data-section-id="ia5moz" data-start="2515" data-end="2546">📎 <strong data-start="2522" data-end="2546">Lampiran (opsional):</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="2547" data-end="2659">
<li data-section-id="2lnew" data-start="2547" data-end="2585">
<p data-start="2550" data-end="2585">Fotokopi identitas diri (KTP/SIM)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4kuzv3" data-start="2586" data-end="2617">
<p data-start="2589" data-end="2617">Bukti tanda terima laporan</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bb3ebm" data-start="2618" data-end="2659">
<p data-start="2621" data-end="2659">Bukti pendukung atau dokumen terkait</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2661" data-end="2664">
<p data-start="2666" data-end="2700">Kalau kamu mau, saya bisa bantu:</p>
<ul data-start="2701" data-end="2905" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">
<li data-section-id="1pv6qpz" data-start="2701" data-end="2905" data-is-last-node="">
<p data-start="2703" data-end="2905" data-is-last-node="">🧾 Menyusun versi <strong data-start="2721" data-end="2766">resmi format surat dinas (Microsoft Word)</strong> dengan tata letak formal, spasi, kop, dan format yang rapi untuk dikirim ke Polda.<br data-start="2849" data-end="2852">
Apakah kamu mau saya buatkan versi Word-nya sekalian?</p>
</li>
</ul></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http