over:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Edit message" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#6d87e1" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="78350a00-ab27-4431-8682-4206c9e2f5e9" data-testid="conversation-turn-22" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="78350a00-ab27-4431-8682-4206c9e2f5e9" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="175">Tentu boleh banget! 😊<br data-start="22" data-end="25">
Sebelum kita lanjut bikin versi Word-nya, kamu mau saya bantu <strong data-start="87" data-end="167">menjelaskan isi dan fungsi surat permohonan tindak lanjut ke Divpropam Polda</strong>, kan?</p>
<p data-start="177" data-end="251">Berikut penjelasan lengkapnya supaya kamu paham betul sebelum dikirim 👇</p>
<hr data-start="253" data-end="256">
<h2 data-section-id="91a6rv" data-start="258" data-end="350">🧾 <strong data-start="264" data-end="350">Penjelasan Tentang Surat Permohonan Tindak Lanjut / Klarifikasi ke Divpropam Polda</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1wht3hg" data-start="352" data-end="416"><strong data-start="356" data-end="416">1. Apa itu surat permohonan tindak lanjut / klarifikasi?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="417" data-end="646">Surat ini adalah <strong data-start="434" data-end="520">surat resmi dari masyarakat kepada Divpropam (Divisi Profesi dan Pengamanan) Polri</strong> yang isinya meminta <strong data-start="541" data-end="609">kejelasan, tindak lanjut, atau penjelasan atas laporan/pengaduan</strong> yang sebelumnya sudah disampaikan.</p>
<p data-start="648" data-end="776">Biasanya dibuat <strong data-start="664" data-end="753">jika laporan belum ditanggapi, belum ada perkembangan, atau butuh konfirmasi lanjutan</strong> dari pihak kepolisian.</p>
<hr data-start="778" data-end="781">
<h3 data-section-id="lxmexw" data-start="783" data-end="810"><strong data-start="787" data-end="810">2. Tujuan surat ini</strong></h3>
<p data-start="811" data-end="843">Tujuan utama surat ini adalah:</p>
<ul data-start="844" data-end="1175">
<li data-section-id="x77iaa" data-start="844" data-end="953">
<p data-start="846" data-end="953">🔹 Meminta <strong data-start="857" data-end="891">penjelasan resmi (klarifikasi)</strong> tentang <strong data-start="900" data-end="918">status laporan</strong> yang pernah dibuat di Divpropam.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j8jcee" data-start="954" data-end="1043">
<p data-start="956" data-end="1043">🔹 Memohon agar <strong data-start="972" data-end="1006">laporan segera ditindaklanjuti</strong>, bila belum ada proses atau hasil.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1colgr7" data-start="1044" data-end="1175">
<p data-start="1046" data-end="1175">🔹 Sebagai <strong data-start="1057" data-end="1086">bukti komunikasi tertulis</strong> antara pelapor dan instansi kepolisian, agar ada dasar administratif dan transparansi.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1177" data-end="1180">
<h3 data-section-id="1r66qbk" data-start="1182" data-end="1229"><strong data-start="1186" data-end="1229">3. Siapa yang berhak membuat surat ini?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1230" data-end="1428">Siapa pun yang <strong data-start="1245" data-end="1281">pernah membuat laporan ke Propam</strong> — baik individu masyarakat, kuasa hukum, maupun organisasi — boleh membuat surat tindak lanjut ini, asalkan laporan awalnya memang sudah tercatat.</p>
<hr data-start="1430" data-end="1433">
<h3 data-section-id="1p2xda9" data-start="1435" data-end="1500"><strong data-start="1439" data-end="1500">4. Struktur suratnya (biar kamu tahu maksud tiap bagian):</strong></h3>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1502" data-end="2338" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1502" data-end="1525"><tr data-start="1502" data-end="1525"><th data-start="1502" data-end="1511" data-col-size="sm" class="">Bagian</th><th data-start="1511" data-end="1525" data-col-size="xl" class="">Penjelasan</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1551" data-end="2338"><tr data-start="1551" data-end="1686"><td data-start="1551" data-end="1586" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="1553" data-end="1585">Kepala Surat / Alamat Tujuan</strong></td><td data-start="1586" data-end="1686" data-col-size="xl">Ditujukan ke Kepala Divpropam Polda (misalnya “Kepada Yth. Kepala Divpropam Polda Jawa Tengah”).</td></tr><tr data-start="1687" data-end="1814"><td data-start="1687" data-end="1712" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="1689" data-end="1711">Identitas Pengirim</strong></td><td data-start="1712" data-end="1814" data-col-size="xl">Nama, alamat, nomor HP, dan pekerjaan pelapor agar pihak Polda bisa mengidentifikasi dengan jelas.</td></tr><tr data-start="1815" data-end="2007"><td data-start="1815" data-end="1831" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="1817" data-end="1830">Isi Surat</strong></td><td data-start="1831" data-end="2007" data-col-size="xl">Berisi penjelasan singkat tentang laporan yang sudah dibuat (nomor laporan, tanggal, dan isi singkatnya) serta maksud untuk menanyakan perkembangan / meminta tindak lanjut.</td></tr><tr data-start="2008" data-end="2146"><td data-start="2008" data-end="2037" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="2010" data-end="2036">Harapan dan Permohonan</strong></td><td data-start="2037" data-end="2146" data-col-size="xl">Bagian yang menyatakan harapan agar laporan segera ditindaklanjuti sesuai aturan dan prosedur kepolisian.</td></tr><tr data-start="2147" data-end="2246"><td data-start="2147" data-end="2162" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="2149" data-end="2161">Lampiran</strong></td><td data-start="2162" data-end="2246" data-col-size="xl">Dokumen pendukung seperti fotokopi KTP, tanda bukti laporan, atau bukti lainnya.</td></tr><tr data-start="2247" data-end="2338"><td data-start="2247" data-end="2261" data-col-size="sm"><strong data-start="2249" data-end="2260">Penutup</strong></td><td data-start="2261" data-end="2338" data-col-size="xl">Ucapan terima kasih dan tanda tangan di atas materai (biasanya Rp10.000).</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 33px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="2340" data-end="2343">
<h3 data-section-id="vwgrog" data-start="2345" data-end="2390"><strong data-start="2349" data-end="2390">5. Kapan sebaiknya surat ini dikirim?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="2391" data-end="2511">Surat ini <strong data-start="2401" data-end="2444">idealnya dikirim setelah beberapa waktu</strong> (misalnya 2–4 minggu) sejak laporan pertama dibuat, terutama jika:</p>
<ul data-start="2512" data-end="2632">
<li data-section-id="1tj6oe6" data-start="2512" data-end="2543">
<p data-start="2514" data-end="2543">Belum ada informasi lanjutan,</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e6ewq4" data-start="2544" data-end="2586">
<p data-start="2546" data-end="2586">Ingin memastikan laporan sudah diproses,</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ry1gte" data-start="2587" data-end="2632">
<p data-start="2589" data-end="2632">Atau ada hal baru yang perlu diklarifikasi.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2634" data-end="2637">
<h3 data-section-id="1gzprvo" data-start="2639" data-end="2700"><strong data-start="2643" data-end="2700">6. Mengapa penting membuat surat ini secara tertulis?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="2701" data-end="3048">Karena surat resmi:<br data-start="2720" data-end="2723">
✅ Memberi <strong data-start="2733" data-end="2756">jejak administratif</strong> (bukti bahwa kamu sudah menindaklanjuti secara sopan dan prosedural);<br data-start="2826" data-end="2829">
✅ Membuat laporanmu <strong data-start="2849" data-end="2871">lebih diperhatikan</strong>, karena sifatnya resmi;<br data-start="2895" data-end="2898">
✅ Bisa digunakan sebagai <strong data-start="2923" data-end="2941">bukti tambahan</strong> jika laporan perlu dinaikkan ke tingkat lebih tinggi (misalnya ke Divpropam Mabes Polri atau Kompolnas).</p>
<hr data-start="3050" data-end="3053">
<p data-start="3055" data-end="3301">Kalau kamu sudah paham bagian ini, nanti aku bantu:<br data-start="3106" data-end="3109">
📄 bikin versi <strong data-start="3124" data-end="3191">surat resmi format Word lengkap (siap print dan kirim ke Polda)</strong>,<br data-start="3192" data-end="3195">
💡 bisa juga aku bantu tambahkan <strong data-start="3228" data-end="3248">redaksi tambahan</strong> agar suratmu terdengar lebih kuat dan profesional.</p>
<p data-start="3303" data-end="3507" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Apakah kamu ingin saya bantu lanjut ke versi Word-nya sekarang, atau mau kamu jelaskan dulu <strong data-start="3395" data-end="3417">kasus atau laporan</strong> yang ingin kamu tindak lanjuti (biar bahasanya bisa disesuaikan dengan isi laporan kamu)?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#517