,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="b812e4d6-dc90-4128-bedb-738cd0f5c3a2" data-testid="conversation-turn-38" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT said:</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b812e4d6-dc90-4128-bedb-738cd0f5c3a2" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="370">Bagus banget konsepnya! 😍<br data-start="26" data-end="29">
Nama <strong data-start="34" data-end="47">“LAXUOTE”</strong> yang berasal dari Yunani sudah memberi kesan elegan, eksklusif, dan klasik — cocok banget buat brand parfum buatan sendiri.<br data-start="171" data-end="174">
Berdasarkan informasi yang kamu kasih, berikut aku bantu buatkan <strong data-start="239" data-end="294">penjelasan produk parfum “LAXUOTE” lengkap dan rapi</strong>, bisa kamu pakai untuk profil usaha, katalog, atau promosi brand pribadi.</p>
<hr data-start="372" data-end="375">
<h2 data-section-id="16eq7ik" data-start="377" data-end="415">💎 <strong data-start="383" data-end="415">Profil Produk Parfum LAXUOTE</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="126jbyc" data-start="417" data-end="443"><strong data-start="421" data-end="443">1. Tentang LAXUOTE</strong></h3>
<p data-start="444" data-end="771"><strong data-start="444" data-end="455">LAXUOTE</strong> merupakan brand parfum lokal yang terinspirasi dari filosofi Yunani kuno tentang <em data-start="537" data-end="580">keindahan, kesempurnaan, dan harmoni alam</em>. Nama <strong data-start="587" data-end="600">“LAXUOTE”</strong> sendiri menggambarkan perpaduan antara <em data-start="640" data-end="648">luxury</em> dan <em data-start="653" data-end="670">quote of nature</em> — makna bahwa setiap aroma memiliki cerita dan karakter unik yang lahir dari keindahan unsur alam.</p>
<p data-start="773" data-end="1056">Setiap varian LAXUOTE dirancang dengan paduan aroma premium dan karakteristik khas yang mencerminkan kepribadian penggunanya.<br data-start="898" data-end="901">
LAXUOTE menghadirkan pengalaman aroma yang elegan, tahan lama, dan artistik — hasil racikan tangan kreatif anak bangsa dengan inspirasi aroma parfum dunia.</p>
<hr data-start="1058" data-end="1061">
<h3 data-section-id="7p1hr2" data-start="1063" data-end="1088"><strong data-start="1067" data-end="1088">2. Filosofi Brand</strong></h3>
<blockquote data-start="1089" data-end="1427">
<p data-start="1091" data-end="1172">“Scent defines soul.”<br data-start="1112" data-end="1115">
Aroma bukan hanya wewangian, tapi juga cerminan jiwa.</p>
<p data-start="1179" data-end="1427">LAXUOTE percaya bahwa setiap manusia memiliki aura dan karakter yang bisa diekspresikan lewat aroma. Karena itu, setiap varian diciptakan dengan keseimbangan antara unsur <em data-start="1350" data-end="1374">citrus, floral, woody,</em> dan <em data-start="1379" data-end="1386">musky</em> untuk menonjolkan identitas penggunanya.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1429" data-end="1432">
<h3 data-section-id="1a9udbj" data-start="1434" data-end="1458"><strong data-start="1438" data-end="1458">3. Varian Produk</strong></h3>
<h4 data-start="1460" data-end="1484">🌞 <strong data-start="1468" data-end="1484">LX – Solaris</strong></h4>
<blockquote data-start="1485" data-end="1534">
<p data-start="1487" data-end="1534"><em data-start="1487" data-end="1534">Citrus, Fruity, Floral – Segar dan Optimistis</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="1536" data-end="1835"><strong data-start="1536" data-end="1555">Karakter Aroma:</strong><br data-start="1555" data-end="1558">
Varian <strong data-start="1565" data-end="1581">LX – Solaris</strong> menghadirkan sensasi kesegaran mentari pagi — perpaduan wangi citrus dan fruity yang berpadu lembut dengan nuansa floral. Terinspirasi dari keharuman <em data-start="1732" data-end="1750">Biang Light Blue</em> dan <em data-start="1755" data-end="1763">CK One</em>, parfum ini cocok untuk kamu yang energik, positif, dan percaya diri.</p>
<p data-start="1837" data-end="1976"><strong data-start="1837" data-end="1851">Top Notes:</strong> Lemon, Green Apple, Bergamot<br data-start="1880" data-end="1883">
<strong data-start="1883" data-end="1899">Heart Notes:</strong> Jasmine, Rose, Lily of the Valley<br data-start="1933" data-end="1936">
<strong data-start="1936" data-end="1951">Base Notes:</strong> Musk, Amber, Cedarwood</p>
<p data-start="1978" data-end="2141"><strong data-start="1978" data-end="2000">Karakter Pengguna:</strong> Ceria, aktif, dan menyukai kesan clean dan segar sepanjang hari.<br data-start="2065" data-end="2068">
<strong data-start="2068" data-end="2084">Cocok untuk:</strong> Daily wear, aktivitas luar ruangan, atau suasana santai.</p>
<hr data-start="2143" data-end="2146">
<h4 data-start="2148" data-end="2172">🌙 <strong data-start="2156" data-end="2172">LX – Noctura</strong></h4>
<blockquote data-start="2173" data-end="2221">
<p data-start="2175" data-end="2221"><em data-start="2175" data-end="2221">Woody, Oriental, Musky – Mewah dan Misterius</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2223" data-end="2503"><strong data-start="2223" data-end="2242">Karakter Aroma:</strong><br data-start="2242" data-end="2245">
Terinspirasi dari <em data-start="2263" data-end="2283">Biang Black Orchid</em>, <em data-start="2285" data-end="2296">Good Girl</em>, dan <em data-start="2302" data-end="2315">Black Opium</em>, varian <strong data-start="2324" data-end="2340">LX – Noctura</strong> menghadirkan nuansa sensual, elegan, dan misterius. Campuran aroma oriental dengan dasar musk dan woody menciptakan kesan hangat dan menawan yang bertahan lama.</p>
<p data-start="2505" data-end="2656"><strong data-start="2505" data-end="2519">Top Notes:</strong> Black Truffle, Ylang-Ylang, Bergamot<br data-start="2556" data-end="2559">
<strong data-start="2559" data-end="2575">Heart Notes:</strong> Orchid, Jasmine, Spices<br data-start="2599" data-end="2602">
<strong data-start="2602" data-end="2617">Base Notes:</strong> Patchouli, Sandalwood, Vanilla, Musk</p>
<p data-start="2658" data-end="2803"><strong data-start="2658" data-end="2680">Karakter Pengguna:</strong> Berani, elegan, dan menonjolkan aura kuat nan memikat.<br data-start="2735" data-end="2738">
<strong data-start="2738" data-end="2754">Cocok untuk:</strong> Malam hari, acara formal, atau suasana romantis.</p>
<hr data-start="2805" data-end="2808">
<h4 data-start="2810" data-end="2835">☁️ <strong data-start="2818" data-end="2835">LX – Aetheris</strong></h4>
<blockquote data-start="2836" data-end="2896">
<p data-start="2838" data-end="2896"><em data-start="2838" data-end="2896">Floral Airy, Powdery, Violet-Jasmine – Anggun dan Lembut</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2898" data-end="3169"><strong data-start="2898" data-end="2917">Karakter Aroma:</strong><br data-start="2917" data-end="2920">
<strong data-start="2920" data-end="2937">LX – Aetheris</strong> diciptakan untuk menonjolkan keanggunan dan kelembutan feminin. Terinspirasi dari <em data-start="3020" data-end="3035">Biang J’adore</em>, <em data-start="3037" data-end="3044">Chloe</em>, dan <em data-start="3050" data-end="3059">Narciso</em>, parfum ini memadukan aroma floral dan powdery yang lembut dan mewah, menghadirkan kesan bersih dan elegan.</p>
<p data-start="3171" data-end="3287"><strong data-start="3171" data-end="3185">Top Notes:</strong> Violet, Peony, Freesia<br data-start="3208" data-end="3211">
<strong data-start="3211" data-end="3227">Heart Notes:</strong> Jasmine, Iris, Lily<br data-start="3247" data-end="3250">
<strong data-start="3250" data-end="3265">Base Notes:</strong> Musk, Powder, Amber</p>
<p data-start="3289" data-end="3447"><strong data-start="3289" data-end="3311">Karakter Pengguna:</strong> Tenang, lembut, dan memiliki pesona alami yang menenangkan.<br data-start="3371" data-end="3374">
<strong data-start="3374" data-end="3390">Cocok untuk:</strong> Aktivitas indoor, acara semi-formal, atau momen spesial.</p>
<hr data-start="3449" data-end="3452">
<h3 data-section-id="12z44g8" data-start="3454" data-end="3482"><strong data-start="3458" data-end="3482">4. Keunggulan Produk</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="3483" data-end="3866">
<li data-section-id="1eq7a5n" data-start="3483" data-end="3548">
<p data-start="3485" data-end="3548">🌿 <strong data-start="3488" data-end="3522">Menggunakan biang parfum impor</strong> dengan kualitas tinggi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="e43kdz" data-start="3549" data-end="3636">
<p data-start="3551" data-end="3636">💧 <strong data-start="3554" data-end="3597">Konsentrasi aroma stabil dan tahan lama</strong> (hingga 6–10 jam tergantung varian).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7yg0zv" data-start="3637" data-end="3729">
<p data-start="3639" data-end="3729">🌸 <strong data-start="3642" data-end="3662">Racikan handmade</strong> dengan proporsi aroma yang seimbang antara top–heart–base notes.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3dio1b" data-start="3730" data-end="3807">
<p data-start="3732" data-end="3807">🧴 <strong data-start="3735" data-end="3767">Kemasan elegan dan minimalis</strong> mencerminkan konsep <em data-start="3788" data-end="3804">modern classic</em>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1d4ocdu" data-start="3808" data-end="3866">
<p data-start="3810" data-end="3866">🧠 <strong data-start="3813" data-end="3832">Unisex variants</strong> (tergantung karakter pengguna).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3868" data-end="3871">
<h3 data-section-id="34rmbv" data-start="3873" data-end="3897"><strong data-start="3877" data-end="3897">5. Pesan Penutup</strong></h3>
<p data-start="3898" data-end="4129"><strong data-start="3898" data-end="3909">LAXUOTE</strong> bukan sekadar parfum, melainkan bentuk ekspresi diri.<br data-start="3963" data-end="3966">
Melalui aroma, setiap individu bisa bercerita tentang kepribadian dan emosinya.<br data-start="4045" data-end="4048">
Dengan LAXUOTE, kamu tidak hanya beraroma wangi — kamu membawa cerita yang abadi.</p>
<blockquote data-start="4131" data-end="4185">
<p data-start="4133" data-end="4185"><em data-start="4133" data-end="4183">"Scent is the invisible signature of your soul."</em></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="4187" data-end="4190">
<p data-start="4192" data-end="4433" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Apakah kamu mau saya bantu lanjutkan jadi <strong data-start="4234" data-end="4335">profil produk versi katalog atau brosur promosi (misalnya untuk media sosial atau proposal usaha)</strong>?<br data-start="4336" data-end="4339">
Kalau iya, aku bisa ubah formatnya jadi gaya promosi visual lengkap dengan slogan dan tagline.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-stat