<hr data-start="2189" data-end="2192">
<h3 data-section-id="90aimh" data-start="2194" data-end="2240">💡 <strong data-start="2201" data-end="2240">Total HPP per botol parfum (30 ml):</strong></h3>
<blockquote data-start="2242" data-end="2308">
<p data-start="2244" data-end="2308"><strong data-start="2244" data-end="2308">Rp42.600 + Rp11.500 + Rp6.000 + Rp3.500 + Rp1.500 = Rp65.100</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2310" data-end="2313">
<h2 data-section-id="16bw6y" data-start="2315" data-end="2348">📦 <strong data-start="2321" data-end="2348">Kesimpulan Perhitungan:</strong></h2>
<ul data-start="2349" data-end="2564">
<li data-section-id="15fch8d" data-start="2349" data-end="2414">
<p data-start="2351" data-end="2414"><strong data-start="2351" data-end="2387">Total HPP (Harga Pokok Produksi)</strong> = <strong data-start="2390" data-end="2412">Rp65.100 per botol</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sc8j8n" data-start="2415" data-end="2564">
<p data-start="2417" data-end="2443"><strong data-start="2417" data-end="2442">Disarankan Harga Jual</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="2446" data-end="2564">
<li data-section-id="18cczdr" data-start="2446" data-end="2508">
<p data-start="2448" data-end="2508">Untuk <strong data-start="2454" data-end="2483">ritel / konsumen langsung</strong>: Rp120.000 – Rp150.000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1e2ne0z" data-start="2511" data-end="2564">
<p data-start="2513" data-end="2564">Untuk <strong data-start="2519" data-end="2540">reseller / grosir</strong>: Rp90.000 – Rp100.000</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2566" data-end="2699">Dengan kisaran harga jual tersebut, kamu akan mendapat <strong data-start="2621" data-end="2649">margin keuntungan 40–60%</strong>, tergantung strategi pasar dan volume produksi.</p>
<hr data-start="2701" data-end="2704">
<h2 data-section-id="1aod9r" data-start="2706" data-end="2733">🧾 <strong data-start="2712" data-end="2733">Catatan Tambahan:</strong></h2>
<ul data-start="2734" data-end="3088">
<li data-section-id="i97bpo" data-start="2734" data-end="2839">
<p data-start="2736" data-end="2839">Jika kamu membeli bahan dalam jumlah besar (literan untuk biang &amp; etanol), <strong data-start="2811" data-end="2836">HPP bisa turun 10–15%</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ljpwki" data-start="2840" data-end="2980">
<p data-start="2842" data-end="2980">Box GSM 350–400 cocok untuk kesan <em data-start="2876" data-end="2884">luxury</em>, bisa ditambah <strong data-start="2900" data-end="2949">finishing emboss, hotstamp gold, atau UV spot</strong> agar tampil lebih eksklusif.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1btp4t5" data-start="2981" data-end="3088">
<p data-start="2983" data-end="3088">Kamu bisa buat varian ukuran mini (10–15 ml) untuk tester, HPP-nya sekitar Rp25.000–Rp30.000 per botol.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3090" data-end="3093">
<p data-start="3095" data-end="3322" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Kalau kamu mau, aku bisa bantu <strong data-start="3126" data-end="3199">lanjutkan dengan format tabel HPP versi laporan kewirausahaan lengkap</strong> (yang ada kolom <em data-start="3216" data-end="3273">harga total produksi per 100 botol, keuntungan, dan BEP</em>).<br data-start="3275" data-end="3278">
Apakah kamu mau saya buatkan versi itu juga?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-