-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="b8c95f34-4a8b-4947-b352-1dd347ec0981" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="78">Bisa banget! 💡<br data-start="15" data-end="18">
HPP parfum <em data-start="29" data-end="38">LAXUOTE</em> itu sangat fleksibel tergantung dari:</p>
<ul data-start="79" data-end="186">
<li data-section-id="20w5tp" data-start="79" data-end="98">
<p data-start="81" data-end="98">skala produksi,</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8vxyw0" data-start="99" data-end="139">
<p data-start="101" data-end="139">bahan yang dipilih (lokal vs impor),</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lulix" data-start="140" data-end="186">
<p data-start="142" data-end="186">serta jenis botol dan box yang kamu pakai.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="188" data-end="365">Kalau kamu ingin <strong data-start="205" data-end="252">HPP lebih murah tapi tetap kelihatan elegan</strong>, kita bisa optimalkan dengan <strong data-start="282" data-end="327">menekan biaya kemasan dan bahan pendukung</strong>, tanpa mengorbankan kualitas aroma.</p>
<p data-start="367" data-end="432">Berikut versi <strong data-start="381" data-end="427">HPP hemat namun tetap premium look (30 ml)</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="434" data-end="437">
<h2 data-section-id="6p046a" data-start="439" data-end="502">💰 <strong data-start="445" data-end="500">HPP Parfum LAXUOTE (Versi Ekonomis &amp; Elegan, 30 ml)</strong></h2>
