<hr data-start="157" data-end="160">
<h3 data-section-id="1sigwzp" data-start="162" data-end="233">💄 <strong data-start="169" data-end="233">HPP Produk Parfum “LAXUOTE” (30 ml – Versi Ekonomis Premium)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="235" data-end="267"><strong data-start="235" data-end="265">1️⃣ Bahan Utama (Rp26.900)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="268" data-end="392">
<li data-section-id="88nesn" data-start="268" data-end="319">
<p data-start="270" data-end="319">Biang parfum lokal (10 ml × Rp2.500) → Rp25.000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ek582q" data-start="320" data-end="344">
<p data-start="322" data-end="344">Etanol 96% → Rp1.200</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rg2umc" data-start="345" data-end="371">
<p data-start="347" data-end="371">Fixative (DPG) → Rp600</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vzluln" data-start="372" data-end="392">
<p data-start="374" data-end="392">Aquadest → Rp100</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="394" data-end="428"><strong data-start="394" data-end="426">2️⃣ Kemasan Primer (Rp7.300)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="429" data-end="524">
<li data-section-id="ksunmr" data-start="429" data-end="459">
<p data-start="431" data-end="459">Botol kaca 30 ml → Rp5.000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17qdbj0" data-start="460" data-end="492">
<p data-start="462" data-end="492">Tutup spray silver → Rp1.500</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="17lq7ft" data-start="493" data-end="524">
<p data-start="495" data-end="524">Label stiker glossy → Rp800</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="526" data-end="562"><strong data-start="526" data-end="560">3️⃣ Kemasan Sekunder (Rp3.500)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="563" data-end="636">
<li data-section-id="4kavva" data-start="563" data-end="605">
<p data-start="565" data-end="605">Box karton art paper 300 GSM → Rp3.000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rp48n5" data-start="606" data-end="636">
<p data-start="608" data-end="636">Cetak logo standar → Rp500</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="638" data-end="677"><strong data-start="638" data-end="675">4️⃣ Overhead &amp; Produksi (Rp2.000)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="678" data-end="715">
<li data-section-id="1mhglcx" data-start="678" data-end="715">
<p data-start="680" data-end="715">Tenaga kerja, listrik, alat bantu</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="717" data-end="720">
<h3 data-section-id="wi9l87" data-start="722" data-end="762">💰 <strong data-start="729" data-end="762">Total HPP per Botol: Rp39.700</strong></h3>
<p data-start="764" data-end="793"><strong data-start="764" data-end="791">Rekomendasi Harga Jual:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="794" data-end="912">
<li data-section-id="1esdme" data-start="794" data-end="832">
<p data-start="796" data-end="832">Retail: Rp85.000 → Keuntungan ±53%</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fyzd0s" data-start="833" data-end="873">
<p data-start="835" data-end="873">Reseller: Rp70.000 → Keuntungan ±43%</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7ssssp" data-start="874" data-end="912">
<p data-start="876" data-end="912">Grosir: Rp60.000 → Keuntungan ±34%</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="914" data-end="917">
<h3 data-section-id="fadv1r" data-start="919" data-end="953">📦 <strong data-start="926" data-end="953">Tips Efisiensi Produksi</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="954" data-end="1143">
<li data-section-id="9s8e0f" data-start="954" data-end="1036">
<p data-start="956" data-end="1036">Beli bahan dalam jumlah besar (biang, botol, box) → HPP bisa turun ke Rp33.000</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ix1wtm" data-start="1037" data-end="1089">
<p data-start="1039" data-end="1089">Gunakan box kraft 250 GSM (eco friendly &amp; murah)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1100r8k" data-start="1090" data-end="1143">
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1143">Cetak label sendiri dengan printer + stiker vinyl</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1145" data-end="1148">
<p data-start="1150" data-end="1308" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Kalau kamu mau, aku bisa bantu buatkan <strong data-start="1189" data-end="1234">slide PowerPoint-nya langsung (3–4 slide)</strong> dengan desain elegan sesuai brand <em data-start="1269" data-end="1278">LAXUOTE</em>. Mau saya bantu buatkan juga?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" 