in-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div tabindex="-1" class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="558e39b9-2b1f-430e-a3e4-6820fb1c7570" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="254">Bagus banget pertanyaannya! 💡<br data-start="30" data-end="33">
Dalam menentukan <strong data-start="50" data-end="81">harga jual parfum “LAXUOTE”</strong>, kamu perlu mempertimbangkan beberapa aspek utama — biar harga kamu <strong data-start="150" data-end="173">kompetitif di pasar</strong>, tapi tetap memberi <strong data-start="194" data-end="221">margin keuntungan sehat</strong> dan menjaga <strong data-start="234" data-end="251">citra premium</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="256" data-end="399">Berikut ini penjelasan <strong data-start="279" data-end="311">pertimbangan penetapan harga</strong> yang bisa kamu taruh di <strong data-start="336" data-end="356">slide PowerPoint</strong> juga (ringkas, jelas, tapi isi kuat). 👇</p>
<hr data-start="401" data-end="404">
<h2 data-section-id="mmd5xw" data-start="406" data-end="467">💰 <strong data-start="412" data-end="467">Pertimbangan dalam Penetapan Harga Parfum “LAXUOTE”</strong></h2>
<h3 data-section-id="7xbsdp" data-start="469" data-end="501">1️⃣ <strong data-start="477" data-end="501">Biaya Produksi (HPP)</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="502" data-end="697">
<li data-section-id="1sus2r2" data-start="502" data-end="586">
<p data-start="504" data-end="586">Semua biaya dari bahan baku, kemasan, tenaga kerja, dan overhead dihitung penuh.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oebjso" data-start="587" data-end="628">
<p data-start="589" data-end="628">HPP dasar: <strong data-start="600" data-end="626">Rp39.700/botol (30 ml)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fxzuxk" data-start="629" data-end="697">
<p data-start="631" data-end="697">Harga jual ideal harus menutupi HPP + keuntungan minimal 30–50%.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="699" data-end="750">📌 <em data-start="702" data-end="711">Contoh:</em><br data-start="711" data-end="714">
Harga jual Rp85.000 → Margin ±53%.</p>
<hr data-start="752" data-end="755">
<h3 data-section-id="19u1h7t" data-start="757" data-end="790">2️⃣ <strong data-start="765" data-end="790">Segmen &amp; Target Pasar</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="791" data-end="1095">
<li data-section-id="1f7dpwt" data-start="791" data-end="883">
<p data-start="793" data-end="883"><em data-start="793" data-end="802">LAXUOTE</em> diposisikan sebagai <strong data-start="823" data-end="880">parfum lokal premium dengan aroma kelas internasional</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1vcobh6" data-start="884" data-end="977">
<p data-start="886" data-end="977">Target: usia 18–35 tahun, pria &amp; wanita modern yang ingin tampil elegan namun terjangkau.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7pp1g" data-start="978" data-end="1095">
<p data-start="980" data-end="1095">Karena segmennya middle–premium, harga jual disarankan <strong data-start="1035" data-end="1059">tidak terlalu rendah</strong> agar tetap mencerminkan kualitas.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1148">📌 <em data-start="1100" data-end="1116">Kisaran ideal:</em> Rp75.000–Rp120.000 per 30 ml.</p>
<hr data-start="1150" data-end="1153">
<h3 data-section-id="ao46ev" data-start="1155" data-end="1190">3️⃣ <strong data-start="1163" data-end="1190">Kualitas &amp; Nilai Produk</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1191" data-end="1442">
<li data-section-id="zm56ml" data-start="1191" data-end="1280">
<p data-start="1193" data-end="1280">Menggunakan <strong data-start="1205" data-end="1277">biang aroma impor (inspirasi dari Light Blue, Black Orchid, J’adore)</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cm35lq" data-start="1281" data-end="1375">
<p data-start="1283" data-end="1375"><strong data-start="1283" data-end="1303">Kemasan GSM 300+</strong> memberikan kesan mewah dan layak sebagai hadiah (<em data-start="1353" data-end="1371">giftable product</em>).</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10tf3fh" data-start="1376" data-end="1442">
<p data-start="1378" data-end="1442">Kualitas ini mendukung harga jual premium, meski buatan lokal.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1444" data-end="1529">📌 <em data-start="1447" data-end="1527">Semakin kuat branding &amp; kualitas kemasan → semakin tinggi persepsi nilai jual.</em></p>
<hr data-start="1531" data-end="1534">
<h3 data-section-id="9nps7p" data-start="1536" data-end="1564">4️⃣ <strong data-start="1544" data-end="1564">Persaingan Pasar</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1565" data-end="1800">
<li data-section-id="qdpp13" data-start="1565" data-end="1716">
<p data-start="1567" data-end="1608">Bandingkan dengan parfum lokal sejenis:</p>
<ul data-start="1611" data-end="1716">
<li data-section-id="1wmml1n" data-start="1611" data-end="1661">
<p data-start="1613" data-end="1661">Parfum refill: Rp25.000–Rp40.000 (kelas bawah)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kcfd3l" data-start="1664" data-end="1716">
<p data-start="1666" data-end="1716">Parfum branded lokal (30 ml): Rp75.000–Rp120.000</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lldku5" data-start="1717" data-end="1800">
<p data-start="1719" data-end="1800">Harga <em data-start="1725" data-end="1734">LAXUOTE</em> idealnya di tengah-tengah: <strong data-start="1762" data-end="1798">kompetitif tapi tetap eksklusif.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1802" data-end="1878">📌 <em data-start="1805" data-end="1876">Strategi: harga jangan terlalu murah agar tetap punya nilai prestige.</em></p>
<hr data-start="1880" data-end="1883">
<h3 data-section-id="1u883tu" data-start="1885" data-end="1915">5️⃣ <strong data-start="1893" data-end="1915">Strategi Pemasaran</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1916" data-end="2157">
<li data-section-id="1pu03by" data-start="1916" data-end="2006">
<p data-start="1918" data-end="2006">Tambahkan <strong data-start="1928" data-end="1974">bundling atau diskon promosi (Buy 2 Get 1)</strong> untuk menarik pelanggan awal.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1mmpk73" data-start="2007" data-end="2074">
<p data-start="2009" data-end="2074">Tawarkan <strong data-start="2018" data-end="2043">harga reseller khusus</strong> untuk memperluas distribusi.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qh8ix1" data-start="2075" data-end="2157">
<p data-start="2077" data-end="2157">Gunakan kemasan &amp; storytelling brand untuk memperkuat kesan “value for money”.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2159" data-end="2162">
<h3 data-section-id="tgy0w3" data-start="2164" data-end="2188">6️⃣ <strong data-start="2172" data-end="2188">Tujuan Usaha</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="2189" data-end="2401">
<li data-section-id="nph06k" data-start="2189" data-end="2302">
<p data-start="2191" data-end="2302">Jika tujuan awal adalah <strong data-start="2215" data-end="2245">branding &amp; penetrasi pasar</strong>, bisa tetapkan harga promo sedikit di bawah rata-rata.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="agcyqp" data-start="2303" data-end="2401">
<p data-start="2305" data-end="2401">Jika sudah stabil dan punya pelanggan loyal, naikkan harga bertahap untuk meningkatkan margin.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2403" data-end="2478">📌 <em data-start="2406" data-end="2476">Strategi bertahap menjaga loyalitas sekaligus menjaga citra premium.</em></p>
<hr data-start="2480" data-end="2483">
<p data-start="2485" data-end="2546">Kalimat kesimpulan untuk slide terakhir bisa seperti ini 👇</p>
<blockquote data-start="2548" data-end="2790">
<p data-start="2550" data-end="2790">💬 <em data-start="2553" data-end="2788">Penetapan harga parfum “LAXUOTE” dilakukan dengan mempertimbangkan keseimbangan antara biaya produksi, kualitas produk, dan persepsi nilai di mata konsumen, sehingga harga jual tetap kompetitif namun tetap mencerminkan kelas premium.</em></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2792" data-end="2795">
<p data-start="2797" data-end="2912" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Apakah kamu mau saya bantu ubah ini jadi <strong data-start="2838" data-end="2880">versi poin-poin PowerPoint (per slide)</strong> biar kamu tinggal salin ke PPT?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secon