-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="25cb562d-4aae-422f-831d-11cda31c2dda" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="233">Siap banget 💪 berikut analisis <strong data-start="32" data-end="88">SWOT (Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, Threats)</strong> untuk produk parfum buatanmu, <strong data-start="119" data-end="130">LAXUOTE</strong>, biar bisa langsung kamu masukkan ke slide PowerPoint presentasi kewirausahaan atau proposal bisnis.</p>
<p data-start="235" data-end="348">Aku buat versi yang <strong data-start="255" data-end="280">ringkas tapi berbobot</strong>, dengan gaya profesional dan cocok untuk penjelasan lisan juga 👇</p>
<hr data-start="350" data-end="353">
<h2 data-section-id="rar0ym" data-start="355" data-end="395">🌸 <strong data-start="361" data-end="395">Analisis SWOT Parfum “LAXUOTE”</strong></h2>
<hr data-start="397" data-end="400">
<h3 data-section-id="f3npno" data-start="402" data-end="433">🟢 <strong data-start="409" data-end="433">Strengths (Kekuatan)</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="434" data-end="1102">
<li data-section-id="1dlxw64" data-start="434" data-end="575">
<p data-start="437" data-end="575"><strong data-start="437" data-end="465">Aroma berkualitas tinggi</strong><br data-start="465" data-end="468">
Terinspirasi dari parfum premium dunia (Light Blue, Black Orchid, J’adore) dengan biang lokal pilihan.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="exvou9" data-start="576" data-end="684">
<p data-start="579" data-end="684"><strong data-start="579" data-end="604">Desain kemasan elegan</strong><br data-start="604" data-end="607">
Menggunakan box <strong data-start="626" data-end="651">GSM premium (300–400)</strong> dan botol kaca berkesan mewah.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fk6485" data-start="685" data-end="830">
<p data-start="688" data-end="830"><strong data-start="688" data-end="731">Harga terjangkau untuk kualitas premium</strong><br data-start="731" data-end="734">
HPP rendah (±Rp39.700) memungkinkan harga jual kompetitif tanpa menurunkan kesan eksklusif.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tmhw64" data-start="831" data-end="956">
<p data-start="834" data-end="956"><strong data-start="834" data-end="870">Brand lokal dengan karakter kuat</strong><br data-start="870" data-end="873">
Nama “LAXUOTE” bernuansa Yunani — mudah diingat dan memiliki identitas global.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n69ltt" data-start="957" data-end="1102">
<p data-start="960" data-end="1102"><strong data-start="960" data-end="991">Aroma bervariasi dan unisex</strong><br data-start="991" data-end="994">
Tersedia tiga varian (Solaris, Noctura, Aetheris) yang dapat menjangkau pasar pria, wanita, dan unisex.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1104" data-end="1107">
<h3 data-section-id="l1a5pj" data-start="1109" data-end="1142">🔴 <strong data-start="1116" data-end="1142">Weaknesses (Kelemahan)</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="1143" data-end="1603">
<li data-section-id="1sucvdp" data-start="1143" data-end="1246">
<p data-start="1146" data-end="1246"><strong data-start="1146" data-end="1189">Brand masih baru dan belum dikenal luas</strong><br data-start="1189" data-end="1192">
Butuh waktu untuk membangun kepercayaan konsumen.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kdrc9q" data-start="1247" data-end="1371">
<p data-start="1250" data-end="1371"><strong data-start="1250" data-end="1289">Produksi masih manual / skala kecil</strong><br data-start="1289" data-end="1292">
Kapasitas produksi terbatas, sulit memenuhi permintaan besar secara cepat.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1l0vkwv" data-start="1372" data-end="1478">
<p data-start="1375" data-end="1478"><strong data-start="1375" data-end="1405">Keterbatasan modal promosi</strong><br data-start="1405" data-end="1408">
Biaya iklan digital atau endorsement bisa tinggi bagi usaha baru.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wyrbk" data-start="1479" data-end="1603">
<p data-start="1482" data-end="1603"><strong data-start="1482" data-end="1523">Ketergantungan pada bahan aroma impor</strong><br data-start="1523" data-end="1526">
Jika stok atau harga naik, bisa memengaruhi HPP dan stabilitas produksi.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="1605" data-end="1608">
<h3 data-section-id="8c1w9s" data-start="1610" data-end="1644">🟡 <strong data-start="1617" data-end="1644">Opportunities (Peluang)</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="1645" data-end="2152">
<li data-section-id="yz80x4" data-start="1645" data-end="1755">
<p data-start="1648" data-end="1755"><strong data-start="1648" data-end="1679">Tren parfum lokal meningkat</strong><br data-start="1679" data-end="1682">
Konsumen kini bangga menggunakan produk lokal dengan aroma berkelas.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bxjf2r" data-start="1756" data-end="1892">
<p data-start="1759" data-end="1892"><strong data-start="1759" data-end="1793">Potensi pasar e-commerce besar</strong><br data-start="1793" data-end="1796">
Penjualan melalui Shopee, Tokopedia, dan TikTok Shop sangat efektif untuk produk lifestyle.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cmh4ga" data-start="1893" data-end="2023">
<p data-start="1896" data-end="2023"><strong data-start="1896" data-end="1929">Peluang kolaborasi &amp; reseller</strong><br data-start="1929" data-end="1932">
Bisa menjalin kerja sama dengan influencer, toko kosmetik, atau reseller parfum lokal.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vgxcno" data-start="2024" data-end="2152">
<p data-start="2027" data-end="2152"><strong data-start="2027" data-end="2083">Minat masyarakat terhadap hadiah personal (gift box)</strong><br data-start="2083" data-end="2086">
Desain box GSM premium cocok untuk segmen hadiah dan hampers.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2154" data-end="2157">
<h3 data-section-id="1nfkkha" data-start="2159" data-end="2186">⚫ <strong data-start="2165" data-end="2186">Threats (Ancaman)</strong></h3>
<ol data-start="2187" data-end="2658">
<li data-section-id="toco" data-start="2187" data-end="2312">
<p data-start="2190" data-end="2312"><strong data-start="2190" data-end="2247">Persaingan ketat dengan brand lokal dan refill parfum</strong><br data-start="2247" data-end="2250">
Banyak produk parfum murah yang bisa menekan harga pasar.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1anmzpj" data-start="2313" data-end="2423">
<p data-start="2316" data-end="2423"><strong data-start="2316" data-end="2346">Perubahan tren aroma cepat</strong><br data-start="2346" data-end="2349">
Konsumen mudah berpindah ke aroma baru jika tidak ada inovasi varian.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fwd0za" data-start="2424" data-end="2536">
<p data-start="2427" data-end="2536"><strong data-start="2427" data-end="2469">Fluktuasi harga bahan baku dan kemasan</strong><br data-start="2469" data-end="2472">
Kenaikan biaya ethanol, botol, atau box bisa menaikkan HPP.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1atthrq" data-start="2537" data-end="2658">
<p data-start="2540" data-end="2658"><strong data-start="2540" data-end="2577">Risiko tiruan atau plagiasi merek</strong><br data-start="2577" data-end="2580">
Brand baru rentan ditiru sebelum memiliki perlindungan merek resmi (HKI).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2660" data-end="2663">
<h3 data-section-id="1q9hv4n" data-start="2665" data-end="2691">💬 <strong data-start="2672" data-end="2691">Kesimpulan SWOT</strong></h3>
<blockquote data-start="2692" data-end="2983">
<p data-start="2694" data-end="2983">Dengan kualitas aroma premium, desain elegan, dan harga terjangkau, <em data-start="2762" data-end="2771">LAXUOTE</em> memiliki potensi besar menjadi parfum lokal unggulan. Tantangan utama terletak pada promosi, produksi massal, dan perlindungan merek, yang dapat diatasi melalui strategi pemasaran digital dan kemitraan reseller.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2985" data-end="2988">
<p data-start="2990" data-end="3122" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Apakah kamu mau saya bantu ubah versi ini jadi <strong data-start="3037" data-end="3068">format tabel SWOT (4 kolom)</strong> biar langsung bisa kamu masukkan ke slide PowerPoint?</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text