"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"about"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"container section"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Tentang Kami</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>HMI Komisariat FISIP UBK Cabang Jakarta Pusat Utara adalah organisasi mahasiswa yang fokus pada kaderisasi, pengkajian sosial-politik, dan pengabdian masyarakat.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"cards"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h4&gt;</span><span>Visi</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h4&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Mewujudkan kader pemimpin yang berpengetahuan dan beretika.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h4&gt;</span><span>Misi</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h4&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Kaderisasi terstruktur</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Pengembangan kepemimpinan</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Advokasi mahasiswa</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</