</li>
<li data-section-id="166cpvf" data-start="165" data-end="174">
<p data-start="168" data-end="174">Ketik:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="176" data-end="191"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Notepad</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="3" data-start="193" data-end="251">
<li data-section-id="8ndmbr" data-start="193" data-end="230">
<p data-start="196" data-end="230">Nanti muncul aplikasi <strong data-start="218" data-end="229">Notepad</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="179tcj5" data-start="231" data-end="251">
<p data-start="234" data-end="251">Klik <strong data-start="239" data-end="250">Notepad</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="253" data-end="262">Selesai ✔</p>
<hr data-start="264" data-end="267">
<h2 data-section-id="13g8s4c" data-start="269" data-end="294">2️⃣ Lewat Menu Windows</h2>
<ol data-start="295" data-end="433">
<li data-section-id="vxs7ef" data-start="295" data-end="333">
<p data-start="298" data-end="333">Klik <strong data-start="303" data-end="332">Start Menu (logo Windows)</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1dkr83t" data-start="334" data-end="353">
<p data-start="337" data-end="353">Scroll ke bawah.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wk33ij" data-start="354" data-end="412">
<p data-start="357" data-end="412">Cari folder <strong data-start="369" data-end="411">Windows Accessories / Aksesori Windows</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="179tcj5" data-start="413" data-end="433">
<p data-start="416" data-end="433">Klik <strong data-start="421" data-end="432">Notepad</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="435" data-end="438">
<h2 data-section-id="n1wtb5" data-start="440" data-end="469">3️⃣ Cara Super Cepat (Run)</h2>
<ol data-start="470" data-end="486">
<li data-section-id="rx06ua" data-start="470" data-end="486">
<p data-start="473" data-end="486">Tekan tombol:</p>
