<h3 data-section-id="vvhucr" data-start="60" data-end="93">❓ Apakah website bisa diedit?</h3>
<p data-start="94" data-end="190"><strong data-start="94" data-end="116">Bisa. Sangat bisa.</strong><br data-start="116" data-end="119">
Website yang kamu buat itu <strong data-start="146" data-end="177">100% bisa diedit kapan saja</strong> dengan cara:</p>
<ul data-start="192" data-end="264">
<li data-section-id="1ui1avy" data-start="192" data-end="218">
<p data-start="194" data-end="218">buka file <strong data-start="204" data-end="218">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1excr3e" data-start="219" data-end="239">
<p data-start="221" data-end="239">ubah teks / gambar</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1j3qio9" data-start="240" data-end="246">
<p data-start="242" data-end="246">save</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1n4fh5l" data-start="247" data-end="264">
<p data-start="249" data-end="264">refresh browser</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="266" data-end="273">Contoh:</p>
<ul data-start="274" data-end="368">
<li data-section-id="1rv68um" data-start="274" data-end="297">
<p data-start="276" data-end="297">ganti berita kegiatan</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15quvz4" data-start="298" data-end="314">
<p data-start="300" data-end="314">ganti pengurus</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4yp95l" data-start="315" data-end="331">
<p data-start="317" data-end="331">ganti foto LK1</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f7cv3d" data-start="332" data-end="346">
<p data-start="334" data-end="346">ganti kontak</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1v0scbd" data-start="347" data-end="368">
<p data-start="349" data-end="368">tambah halaman baru</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="370" data-end="506">Jadi website organisasi seperti <strong data-start="402" data-end="420">HMI Komisariat</strong> memang biasanya dibuat seperti ini supaya <strong data-start="463" data-end="505">pengurus berikutnya juga bisa mengedit</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="508" data-end="511">
<h1 data-section-id="sh05z7" data-start="513" data-end="549">Kenapa Logo HMI kamu tidak muncul?</h1>
