<hr data-start="1781" data-end="1784">
<h1 data-section-id="1mtw5tt" data-start="1786" data-end="1829">Supaya Website Kamu Kelihatan Profesional</h1>
<p data-start="1830" data-end="1856">Minimal harus ada halaman:</p>
<p data-start="1858" data-end="2063">1️⃣ <strong data-start="1862" data-end="1873">Beranda</strong><br data-start="1873" data-end="1876">
2️⃣ <strong data-start="1880" data-end="1906">Tentang HMI Komisariat</strong><br data-start="1906" data-end="1909">
3️⃣ <strong data-start="1913" data-end="1926">Visi Misi</strong><br data-start="1926" data-end="1929">
4️⃣ <strong data-start="1933" data-end="1954">Struktur Pengurus</strong><br data-start="1954" data-end="1957">
5️⃣ <strong data-start="1961" data-end="1978">Program Kerja</strong><br data-start="1978" data-end="1981">
6️⃣ <strong data-start="1985" data-end="2024">Kegiatan LK1 / Diskusi / Pelantikan</strong><br data-start="2024" data-end="2027">
7️⃣ <strong data-start="2031" data-end="2046">Galeri Foto</strong><br data-start="2046" data-end="2049">
8️⃣ <strong data-start="2053" data-end="2063">Kontak</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2065" data-end="2068">
<h1 data-section-id="o57us9" data-start="2070" data-end="2131">Kalau Kamu Mau, Gue Bisa Buatin Versi yang Jauh Lebih Keren</h1>
<p data-start="2133" data-end="2178">Misalnya website seperti organisasi nasional:</p>
<p data-start="2180" data-end="2184">Ada:</p>
<p data-start="2186" data-end="2376">✅ landing page modern<br data-start="2207" data-end="2210">
✅ warna <strong data-start="2218" data-end="2236">hijau khas HMI</strong><br data-start="2236" data-end="2239">
✅ halaman <strong data-start="2249" data-end="2270">struktur pengurus</strong><br data-start="2270" data-end="2273">
✅ <strong data-start="2275" data-end="2301">pendaftaran LK1 online</strong><br data-start="2301" data-end="2304">
✅ galeri kegiatan<br data-start="2321" data-end="2324">
✅ berita kaderisasi<br data-start="2343" data-end="2346">
✅ tombol <strong data-start="2355" data-end="2376">WhatsApp langsung</strong></p>
<p data-start="2378" data-end="2431">Dan tampilannya <strong data-start="2394" data-end="2430">lebih profesional dari yang tadi</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="2433" data-end="2553" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Kalau kamu mau, bilang aja.<br data-start="2460" data-end="2463">
