pan><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"btn"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">href</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"#kontak"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><span>Hubungi Kami</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"tentang"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"section"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span>Tentang Kami</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><br><span>Himpunan Mahasiswa Islam (HMI) Komisariat FISIP UBK merupakan organisasi mahasiswa yang berfokus pada kaderisasi, pengembangan intelektual, dan pengabdian kepada masyarakat.</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"grid"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Visi</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Mewujudkan kader pemimpin yang berintegritas dan berpengetahuan luas.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Misi</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Mengembangkan kader melalui kegiatan intelektual, sosial, dan kepemimpinan.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;div</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"card"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h3&gt;</span><span>Nilai</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;p&gt;</span><span>Integritas, solidaritas, intelektual, dan profesional.</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"program"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"section"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span>Program Kegiatan</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;ul</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"program"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Latihan Kader 1 (LK1)</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Diskusi Publik dan Kajian Intelektual</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Pengabdian Masyarakat</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;li&gt;</span><span>Pelatihan Kepemimpinan</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/ul&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">id</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"galeri"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼu">class</span><span class="ͼn">=</span><span class="ͼr">"section"</span><span class="ͼv">&gt;</span><br><br><span class="ͼv">&lt;h2&gt;</span><span>Galeri Kegiatan</span><span class="ͼv">&lt;/h2&gt;</span><br>