✔ Program Kegiatan<br data-start="4196" data-end="4199">
✔ Galeri<br data-start="4207" data-end="4210">
✔ Kontak<br data-start="4218" data-end="4221">
✔ Nomor WA kamu <strong data-start="4237" data-end="4253">085718596243</strong></p>
<hr data-start="4255" data-end="4258">
<p data-start="4260" data-end="4346">💡 Kalau kamu mau, gue juga bisa bikin <strong data-start="4299" data-end="4335">versi yang jauh lebih keren lagi</strong>, misalnya:</p>
<ul data-start="4348" data-end="4529">
<li data-section-id="1hyh545" data-start="4348" data-end="4379">
<p data-start="4350" data-end="4379">ada <strong data-start="4354" data-end="4379">struktur pengurus HMI</strong></p>
