<p data-start="130" data-end="153"><code data-start="130" data-end="138">script</code> → JavaScript</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="155" data-end="246">Sekarang tinggal <strong data-start="172" data-end="215">buat folder <code data-start="186" data-end="191">img</code> untuk logo dan gambar</strong> supaya website tampil lengkap.</p>
<hr data-start="248" data-end="251">
<h1 data-section-id="1mzyt5x" data-start="253" data-end="280">Cara Membuat Folder <code data-start="275" data-end="280">img</code></h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1l8wa78" data-start="282" data-end="326">1️⃣ Klik kanan di dalam folder yang sama</h3>
<p data-start="327" data-end="351">Di tempat yang ada file:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="353" data-end="379"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>index</span><br><span>style</span><br><span>script</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="381" data-end="436">klik <strong data-start="386" data-end="400">klik kanan</strong> → pilih <strong data-start="409" data-end="423">New / Baru</strong> → <strong data-start="426" data-end="436">Folder</strong></p>
<hr data-start="438" data-end="441">
