<p data-start="559" data-end="590">➡️ <strong data-start="562" data-end="590">gambar tidak akan muncul</strong></p>
<p data-start="592" data-end="620">Karena nama filenya berbeda.</p>
<hr data-start="622" data-end="625">
<h2 data-section-id="1a7s5vg" data-start="627" data-end="656">Hal yang Harus Sama Persis</h2>
<p data-start="658" data-end="680">Ini harus <strong data-start="668" data-end="679">identik</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="682" data-end="771">
<li data-section-id="czsoot" data-start="682" data-end="697">
<p data-start="684" data-end="697">nama folder</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zqhrf1" data-start="698" data-end="711">
<p data-start="700" data-end="711">nama file</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sdpzo4" data-start="712" data-end="735">
<p data-start="714" data-end="735">huruf besar / kecil</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12egxak" data-start="736" data-end="771">
<p data-start="738" data-end="771">format file (<code data-start="751" data-end="757">.png</code>, <code data-start="759" data-end="765">.jpg</code>, dll)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="773" data-end="786">Contoh benar:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="788" data-end="833"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>img/logo.png</span><br><span>img/logo.jpg</span><br><span>img/hmi.png</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="835" data-end="838">
<h2 data-section-id="1p1qmou" data-start="840" data-end="862">Cara Cepat Mengecek</h2>
<ol data-start="864" data-end="952">
<li data-section-id="14avwnm" data-start="864" data-end="886">
<p data-start="867" data-end="886">Buka folder <strong data-start="879" data-end="886">img</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1f2tszx" data-start="887" data-end="907">
