<hr data-start="954" data-end="957">
<p data-start="959" data-end="989">💡 Tips penting untuk website:</p>
<p data-start="991" data-end="1051">Biasanya developer membuat struktur seperti ini supaya rapi:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1053" data-end="1192"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>website</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── index.html</span><br><span>├── style.css</span><br><span>├── script.js</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>├── img</span><br><span>│   ├── logo.png</span><br><span>│   ├── hero.jpg</span><br><span>│   └── kegiatan1.jpg</span><br><span>│</span><br><span>└── assets</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1194" data-end="1241">Jadi semua gambar <strong data-start="1212" data-end="1240">disimpan di folder <code data-start="1233" data-end="1238">img</code></strong>.</p>
