<h1 data-section-id="mhkuge" data-start="1832" data-end="1872">3️⃣ Tambahkan Style Supaya Profesional</h1>
<p data-start="1874" data-end="1917">Buka <strong data-start="1879" data-end="1892">style.css</strong> lalu tambahkan di bawah.</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1919" data-end="2358"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">struktur-grid</span><span>{</span><br><span>display:</span><span class="ͼq">grid</span><span>;</span><br><span>grid-template-columns:</span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">auto-fit</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼn">minmax</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">220</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>));</span><br><span>gap:</span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>margin-top:</span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">pengurus</span><span>{</span><br><span>background:</span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>padding:</span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>border-radius:</span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>text-align:</span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>box-shadow:</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>,</span><span class="ͼq">0.08</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">pengurus</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">img</span><span>{</span><br><span>width:</span><span class="ͼq">90</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>height:</span><span class="ͼq">90</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>border-radius:</span><span class="ͼq">50</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>object-fit:</span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>margin-bottom:</span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">pengurus</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h4</span><span>{</span><br><span>margin:</span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>color:#005c2e;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">utama</span><span>{</span><br><span>border-top:</span><span class="ͼq">5</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> #005c2e;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2360" data-end="2363">
<h1 data-section-id="hsmwg2" data-start="2365" data-end="2391">4️⃣ Struktur Folder Foto</h1>
<p data-start="2393" data-end="2433">Masukkan foto pengurus ke folder <strong data-start="2426" data-end="2433">img</strong></p>
<p data-start="2435" data-end="2442">Contoh:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2444" data-end="2486"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>img</span><br><span>ketum.jpg</span><br><span>sekum.jpg</span><br><span>bendum.jpg</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2488" data-end="2542">Kalau belum ada foto, bisa pakai <strong data-start="2521" data-end="2541">placeholder dulu</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2544" data-end="2547">
<h1 data-section-id="zwfnql" data-start="2549" data-end="2586">5️⃣ Hasilnya Nanti Akan Seperti Ini</h1>
<p data-start="2588" data-end="2616">Tampilan website kamu nanti:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2618" data-end="2743"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-il7yfj1b.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Ketua Umum        Sekretaris Umum        Bendahara Umum</span><br><br><span>Kabid Kaderisasi  Kabid PTKP             Kabid PPDA</span><br><br><span>Anggota</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2745" data-end="2812">Semua dalam <strong data-start="2757" data-end="2811">card modern seperti website organisasi profesional</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="2814" data-end="2817">
<h1 data-section-id="dvqs3x" data-start="2819" data-end="2865">6️⃣ Upgrade Supaya Website Kamu Level Kampus</h1>
<p data-start="2867" data-end="2947">Kalau kamu mau website <strong data-start="2890" data-end="2927">benar-benar kelihatan profesional</strong>, biasanya ditambah:</p>
<p data-start="2949" data-end="3131">✔ Hero banner kegiatan<br data-start="2971" data-end="2974">
✔ Struktur pengurus dengan foto<br data-start="3005" data-end="3008">
✔ Timeline kegiatan<br data-start="3027" data-end="3030">
✔ Galeri kegiatan<br data-start="3047" data-end="3050">
✔ Form pendaftaran LK1<br data-start="3072" data-end="3075">
✔ Tombol WhatsApp mengambang<br data-start="3103" data-end="3106">
✔ Animasi scroll modern</p>
<p data-start="3133" data-end="3230">Kalau kamu mau, aku bisa bikinin <strong data-start="3166" data-end="3221">versi website komisariat kamu yang jauh lebih keren</strong> seperti:</p>
<ul data-start="3232" data-end="3392">
<li data-section-id="e27dj2" data-start="3232" data-end="3265">
<p data-start="3234" data-end="3265">website <strong data-start="3242" data-end="3265">organisasi nasional</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1whd7cx" data-start="3266" data-end="3292">
<p data-start="3268" data-end="3292">warna <strong data-start="3274" data-end="3292">hijau khas HMI</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4hki7t" data-start="3293" data-end="3323">
<p data-start="3295" data-end="3323"><strong data-start="3295" data-end="3323">struktur pengurus visual</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gwthd" data-start="3324" data-end="3352">
<p data-start="3326" data-end="3352"><strong data-start="3326" data-end="3352">pendaftaran LK1 online</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8qmd0u" data-start="3353" data-end="3392">
<p data-start="3355" data-end="3392"><strong data-start="3355" data-end="3392">langsung bisa diakses di internet</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
